<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-12-1285 </DOCNO><TEXT>Slag-ceramics were produced from glass compositions using pelletized slagas the major ingredient. The abrasion resistance, fracture toughnessand microstructure of the prepared glass and glass-ceramics were evaluated.Glas-ceramics with good abrasion resistance were obtained when iron oxidein conjunction with carbon was used as a nucleating agent. 5 figs., 11tabs.</TEXT></DOC>